===========================================================================

URL for simplify binaries:

http://kindsoftware.com/products/opensource/archives/Simplify-1.5.5-13-06-07-binary.zip

As of 12/11/2014, the zip file is dated 1/2/2012

cd ~/bin/install
wget http://kindsoftware.com/products/opensource/archives/Simplify-1.5.5-13-06-07-binary.zip
unzip Simplify-1.5.5-13-06-07-binary.zip
chmod +x Simplify/Simplify-1.5.4.linux
cd $HOME/bin/`uname`-`uname -m`
ln -s ../install/Simplify/Simplify-1.5.4.linux Simplify

