Old, now-broken link for Simplify binaries from University College Dublin:
https://mobius.ucd.ie/repos/src/simplify/
Rules for getting that binary:
wget --no-check-certificate https://mobius.ucd.ie/repos/src/simplify/Simplify-1.5.4.linux
chmod +x Simplify-1.5.4.linux
# This produced: "Segmentation fault"
